	(gr_text "Why not work?\nUser error.\n\nWhy did it reset itself?\nPersonal reasons.\n\nWhy is it hot?\nThat means it's thinking.\n\nWhy did the screen freeze?\nIt got scared.\n\nWhy does the button do nothing?\nIt's doing its best.\n\nWhy is there smoke?\nSensory feedback.\n\nWhy won't it compile?\nSkill issue.\n\nWhy did it crash?\nIt needed a break."
